{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be dynamic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Financial Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #f06292; /* Lighter Pinkish Red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #fafafa;\n            --dark-text-color: #333333;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .section h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(229, 57, 53, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 500px;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;\n            max-width: 500px;\n            width: 100%;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            opacity: 0.85;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            .section h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Apex Financial Consulting</h1>\n        <p>Your trusted partner for strategic financial guidance and growth.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n        <section class=\"container section\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    <h3>Investment Strategy</h3>\n                    <p>Tailored strategies to grow your wealth and achieve financial goals.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-handshake\"></i>\n                    <h3>Corporate Finance</h3>\n                    <p>Expert advice on mergers, acquisitions, and capital raising.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-calculator\"></i>\n                    <h3>Risk Management</h3>\n                    <p>Protecting your assets with robust risk assessment and mitigation.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                    <h3>Personal Finance</h3>\n                    <p>Guidance for individuals to build a secure financial future.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"container section\">\n            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em;\">At Apex Financial Consulting, we are dedicated to providing clear, actionable insights. Our experienced team combines deep market knowledge with a personalized approach to ensure your financial success. We pride ourselves on transparency, integrity, and delivering measurable results.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"container section\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form class=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Financial Consulting. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelector('.contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Message sent! Thank you for contacting Apex Financial Consulting.');\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}